{"tid":694665,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大哥哥叫我幫他…李依瑾爆險遭性侵 主持人突問「他帥嗎？」掀眾怒","createTime":"2018-06-08T13:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T14:26:12.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60afcfebd7e49fe923fa918cc6d4cb4bd1170508","tid":694665,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pLt8n0RDmeQaoDnS1bI8Zg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTIwMDtoPTY3NQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/e7f34ee71cbfac9de9fcf8ff998b6a79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpLt8n0RDmeQaoDnS1bI8Zg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTIwMDtoPTY3NQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2Fe7f34ee71cbfac9de9fcf8ff998b6a79&h=d90d1274&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女星李依瑾兼具甜美外表與清新脫俗的氣質，近日上節目自爆小時候差點慘遭鄰居大哥哥性侵的回憶，不僅導致她長期飽受憂鬱症所苦，也讓她出現了社交障礙，甚至做出傷害自己的動作，經常將身體摳到受傷流血，當她勇敢地說出這段夢魘時，主持人利菁竟突然吐出一句：「他（大哥哥）帥嗎？」讓現場氣氛瞬間沉默凍結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kLP_8y2qKfi.vB4B6n2Qtw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODcyO2g9NDgx/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/c4a9c571de25856b1c6395f7ac1e1ae2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkLP_8y2qKfi.vB4B6n2Qtw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODcyO2g9NDgx%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2Fc4a9c571de25856b1c6395f7ac1e1ae2&h=75498f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李依瑾在節目《麻辣天后傳》上討論憂鬱症的主題，自爆她7歲正就讀小學二年級時，某天放學後，在公寓大門前遇見一位陌生的大哥哥詢問是否可以到她家借廁所，沒想到對方接著要求她「幫忙」許多事，當時年紀幼小的她也都乖乖照做，直到自己感覺到有點不舒服，她腦中突然想起了老師曾跟她說過，遇到類似的事情時，可以跟對方表明爸媽快回家了，「那個大哥哥才趕快穿好褲子。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yKxglT5CzOdToUVM2Z8Hsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODkwO2g9NTE0/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ebc.net.tw/03798b495e3fc7eb5c9b3476bb80b295\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyKxglT5CzOdToUVM2Z8Hsw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODkwO2g9NTE0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Febc.net.tw%2F03798b495e3fc7eb5c9b3476bb80b295&h=24197655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後，李依瑾還送那位大哥哥出門，「沒想到他不是往樓下走，而是往我家樓上走，他是我家樓上的大哥哥。就在這一刻，我對人的信任完全沒有了。」可怕的回憶讓她直到現在，仍對於「人」依然心懷恐懼與不安。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1834/d1834231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1834%2Fd1834231.jpg&h=5c912975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李依瑾如今回想起這段不堪的回憶時，「發生事情的時候，妳完全不會討厭、不會生氣，因為妳會覺得我是在幫他。」只見李依瑾帶著忍不住顫抖的聲音說出這段過去，讓現場來賓聽了滿是心疼，未料正當她講到一半時，利菁突然打斷談話、蹦出一句：「他帥嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2015/03/02/227468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2015%2F03%2F02%2F227468.jpg&h=e8543ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李依瑾聽到利菁的問題後，整個人也傻住了幾秒時間，神情看似淡定地繼續將故事給說完。網友看到這個片段時，怒轟利菁問話超不禮貌，「菁姊蠻沒禮貌的，一直打斷來賓說話」、「利菁竟然問李那個變態帥嗎？瘋了嗎！這種心理話題真的要謹慎小心每一字、每一句啊」，許多網友則是為李依瑾所遭遇恐怖的經歷獻上加油打氣。"},{"pid":"49e44c206e89453318ca2b40dc95e7b01032800c","tid":694665,"uid":68219,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話</span></span>"},{"pid":"5fb8ec6b5809209153bfc5cfc1d3455a7651b1e9","tid":694665,"uid":32952,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:54:20.000Z","msg":"無朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53d5ae23490b0023f289cd305877525660d2232","tid":694665,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e44c206e89453318ca2b40dc95e7b01032800c","tid":694665,"uid":68219,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-